      "last_modified": "2021-04-20T15:12:14",
      "page_number": 8,
      "parent_id": "eba69bc6b1f458292f20d7a1ef04d697",
      "filetype": "application/pdf"
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "ListItem",
    "element_id": "219da98aa33435a241077cd34517e4eb",
    "text": "We can build such a sensor using photodiodes. \u2022 Let\u2019s suppose the track is painted with a light- reflecting color, whereas the floor is relatively dark.",
